I will modify the `getInsertPoint` function. I'll add a loop at the beginning to check for `Argument`s in `Roots`. If an `Argument` is found, I'll set the insertion point to the beginning of the entry block of the argument's parent function and return immediately. This is the safest and most correct behavior.

